1084
00:43:12,217 --> 00:43:14,384
There must be a reason for that, no?

1085
00:43:14,419 --> 00:43:16,251
Perhaps you are an expert.

1086
00:43:17,651 --> 00:43:20,184
Uh, that's it, Mr. Oldman.
