00:46:06,019 --> 00:46:08,382
He struck back expertly.

1142
00:46:08,417 --> 00:46:11,183
That stuff about stealing life forces?

1143
00:46:11,218 --> 00:46:13,950
I've always wondered about the reasons.

1144
00:46:20,317 --> 00:46:23,618
Well, we still have an
afternoon to kill, right?

