for years with the blowing.

1164
00:47:15,917 --> 00:47:17,882
Yeah, all right. I tried.

1165
00:47:17,917 --> 00:47:21,184
Well, uh, call me underdeveloped,

1166
00:47:21,219 --> 00:47:23,551
but I'd like to hear more.

1167
00:47:25,783 --> 00:47:27,100
Me too.

1168
00:47:27,135 --> 00:47:28,382
More.

1169
00:47:28,417 --> 00:47:30,783
You double-damn swear
this isn't some cockamamie

1170
00:47:30,818 --> 00:47:32,984
science fiction story or...

1171
00:47:33,019 --> 00:47:34,351
you're pulling on us?

1172
00:47:34,386 --> 00:47:36,848
Next question.

1173
00:47:36,883 --> 00:47:38,217
You-You-You realize

1174
00:47:38,252 --> 00:47:39,516
this is an invitation

1175
