1311
00:52:34,852 --> 00:52:36,684
and there are earlier versions.

1312
00:52:36,719 --> 00:52:38,482
All found floating on water,

1313
00:52:38,517 --> 00:52:41,050
the staff that changed to a snake,

1314
00:52:41,085 --> 00:52:43,584
waters that were parted so followers

1315
00:52:43,619 --> 00:52:45,151
could be led to freedom

1316
00:52:45,186 --> 00:52:46,649
and even receive laws

1317
00:52:46,684 --> 00:52:48,251
on stone or wooden tablets.

1318
00:52:48,286 --> 00:52:51,149
One of the apostles.

1319
00:52:51,184 --> 00:52:53,600
They weren't really apostles.

1320
00:52:53,635 --> 00:52:55,982
They didn't do any real teaching.

1321
00:52:56,017 --> 00:52:59,317
Peter the fisherman learned
a little more about fishing.

1322
00:52:59,352 --> 00:53:01,351
How do you know that?

1323
00:53:03,783 --> 00:53:06,750
The mythical overlay is so enormous...

1324
00:53:08,150 --> 00:53:10,182
and not good.

1325
00:53:10,217 --> 00:53:16,382
The truth is so, so simple.

1326
00:53:16,417 --> 00:53:20,117
The New Testament in 100
words or less: you ready?

1327
00:53:20,152 --> 00:53:21,718
I don't think I wanna hear this.

