00:53:21,753 --> 00:53:23,249
Harry, will you take me home?

1329
00:53:23,284 --> 00:53:25,115
No, not right now.
I do want to hear this.

1330
00:53:25,150 --> 00:53:27,517
Sit down, Edith.
You act like you believe him.

1331
00:53:27,552 --> 00:53:28,915
It's sacrilege.

1332
00:53:28,950 --> 00:53:30,149
How can it be sacrilege?

1333
00:53:30,184 --> 00:53:31,282
